Okhulumela inkampani yonogada bakwaReactions Unit of South Africa (Rusa), uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe onogada babo namaphoyisa iSAPS bafike endaweni yesehlakalo emuva kokulunywa indlebe unogada obegade kule ndawo mayelana namadoda abezama ukweba amabhethri ombhoshongo. “Amaphoyisa afike athola ukuthi kunabasolwa abathathu abagqekeza lo mbhoshongo osehlane, ophakathi emasimini omoba. Ngesikhathi kutheleka onogada abasolwa bebesematasa bezama ukuntshontsha amabhethri okusolwa ukuthi ngesikhathi bebona onogada, bavele bavulela ngenhlamvu bebhikise kubo okuphoqe onogada namaphoyisa ukuthi baphendule ngenhlamvu bebhekise kubasolwa,” kusho uBalram. Uthe umsolwa oyedwa udubuleke kabili esifubeni wafa endaweni yesigameko. Uthe abanye abasolwa ababili babaleke ngezinyawo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, usiqinisekisile isigameko. “Kuvulwe idokodo ngokufa komuntu necala lokuzama ukubulala esiteshini samaphoyisa eVerulam. Amaphoyisa ayaphenya,” kusho uColonel Mbele